      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray in the oven for 14-15 min or until the salmon is cooked through and the crumb is crisp and golden – this is your <strong>herb-crusted salmon</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>blanched</strong> <strong>peas</strong> to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water </strong>and cook on a high heat for 1 min or until they're tender</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return the peas to the pot</p>",
