    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crush the<strong> refreshed peas </strong>roughly<strong> </strong>with a potato<strong> </strong>masher</p><p>Stir your <strong>soft cheese</strong>, the juice of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>lemon[s] </strong>(not sure about citrus? Try using less!) and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>through the <strong>crushed peas</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, then warm through over a medium heat for 2 min – these are your <strong>creamy crushed peas</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
